data.description: Very nice brick home in desirable area. Home has many recent upgrades, including roof, plumbing, water heater, bathrooms, windows and dishwasher to name a few. You will enjoy both a living room (main level) and a family room (downstairs) each has a fireplace. Basement also has lots of storage areas, office room and a bedroom with egress window. Spacious 2 car garage with front and back man door. Don't wait to see this home. Has an assumable loan!
